title: S12 Ep183: Sasquatch Is My Healer
itunes:title: Sasquatch Is My Healer
description:
Samara Terpening had many physical ailments the day she went out target shooting with her husband. It was that day in the woods, that she had her first experience with Sasquatch. What she didn't bargain for, was Sasquatch healing her ailments and... teaching her to heal others?
